<td id="D0E11ABAFD29DF1DEDCD3A29BA66F45D" colspan="1" pageId="7" pageNumber="406" rowspan="1">Pronotum broadly cordate, relatively short and broad (W pn wp/L pn = 1.40-1.55), elytral interval 1 black, or at least distinctly darker than intervals 2-8, at least in basal 1/3</td>
